==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|ML.|en}} {{term|simultaneus|lang=la}}, from {{term|simultim||at the same time, extended|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|simul||together, at the same time|lang=la}}; compare [[similar]].

