* {{a|UK}} {{IPA|/sɪm.əlˈteɪ̯n.i.əs/}}
* {{a|US}} {{IPA|/ˌsaɪ̯m.əlˈteɪ̯n.i.əs/}}
* {{rhymes|eɪniəs}}
* {{rhymes|eɪnɪəs}}

===Adjective===
{{en-adj|-}}

# [[occur|Occurring]] or [[transpire|transpiring]] at the same [[time]].
